## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b911f-307">所傳回的物件的基礎類型<xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlDocument.InvokeScript%2A>而異。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b911f-307">The underlying type of the object returned by <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlDocument.InvokeScript%2A> will vary.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b911f-308">如果呼叫的 Active Scripting 函式會傳回純量的資料，例如字串或整數，它會當做字串傳回。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b911f-308">If the called Active Scripting function returns scalar data, such as a string or an integer, it will be returned as a string.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b911f-309">如果它傳回指令碼為基礎物件，例如使用 JScript 或 VBScript 的建立物件`new`運算子，它將會是類型`Object`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b911f-309">If it returns a script-based object, such as an object created using JScript or VBScript's `new` operator, it will be of type `Object`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b911f-310">(您也可以呼叫這類物件上進行呼叫<xref:System.Object.GetType%2A>和使用<xref:System.Type.InvokeMember%2A>。)如果它傳回的 HTML DOM 項目，例如`DIV`或`TABLE`，其類型會是`Object`; 如果您已經加入 MSHTML 的專案參考。DLL，不過，它會轉換為其特定 unmanaged DOM 型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b911f-310">(You can make calls on such objects by calling <xref:System.Object.GetType%2A> and using <xref:System.Type.InvokeMember%2A>.) If it returns an HTML DOM element, such as a `DIV` or a `TABLE`, it will be of type `Object`; if you have added a project reference to MSHTML.DLL, however, it will be cast to its specific unmanaged DOM type.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="b911f-311">您可能會呼叫使用者的電腦，包括 JScript 和 VBScript 上安裝任何使用中指令碼語言撰寫的任何函式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b911f-311">You may call any function written in any Active Scripting language installed on the user's computer, including JScript and VBScript.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="b911f-312"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlDocument.InvokeScript%2A>不致 nothing 如果使用者已明確關閉 Internet Explorer 中指令碼執行，或網頁的目前安全性組態不允許使用它。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b911f-312">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlDocument.InvokeScript%2A> will do nothing if the user has explicitly turned off script execution in Internet Explorer, or if the current security configuration for the Web page does not allow it.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b911f-313">下列程式碼範例會執行指令碼的內容在網頁中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b911f-313">The following code example executes the contents of a script in a Web page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b911f-314">程式碼範例需要您具有<xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser>呼叫的應用程式中`WebBrowser1`，及您已載入下列網頁。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b911f-314">The code example requires that you have a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> in your application called `WebBrowser1`, and that you have loaded the following Web page.</span></span>  

```  
<HTML>  

    <HEAD>  
        <TITLE>Invoke Script Sample</TITLE>  

        <SCRIPT>  
            function MyObject() {  
                this.Data = "Data for my private object.";  
            }  
            // Return a string.  
            function test() {  
                return("This is a test.");  
            }  
            // Return a JScript object.  
            function testJScriptObject() {  
                return(new(MyObject));  
            }  
            // Return a DOM element.  
            function testElement() {  
                return(div1);  
            }  
        </SCRIPT>  
    </HEAD>  

    <BODY>  

        <DIV id="div1">  
        </DIV>  

    </BODY>  

</HTML>  

```  

